{"tid":97662,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊兩年，分開年半","createTime":"2017-01-27T20:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T04:01:16.000Z","uid":14015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8549d0b49fd4ddb07c508d3d6935a519bc70b0","tid":97662,"uid":14015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:01:29.000Z","msg":"究竟係咩，令到回憶仲會不時纏繞著自己<br />\n遺憾，放唔低，定還是始終未講完自己既感受<br />\n<br />\n所謂回憶者，雖說可以使人歡欣，有時也不免使人寂寞，使精神的絲縷還牽著己逝的寂寞的時光，又有甚麼意味呢，而我偏苦於不能全忘卻，這不能全忘的一部分。"},{"pid":"6348d69bffd3b2727e5f8183ed792b832518aeba","tid":97662,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:12:10.000Z","msg":"當你幻想下對方可能已經完全放低，甚至遺忘左你，就會覺得自己嘅執著好on9"},{"pid":"5f7a66674c8ac9a3ea70da78d8510fba2ba8c42f","tid":97662,"uid":14015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你幻想下對方可能已經完全放低，甚至遺忘左你，就會覺得自己嘅執著好on9</blockquote><br />\n又講唔上執着既，只係好感慨<br />\n時不時會諗起，會夢見<br />\n好似不斷提醒你，身邊曾經出現過呢個人咁<br />\n可能大家已經成為左陌生人，<br />\n但係回憶始終會縈繞係心底裡面"},{"pid":"419a1cc86efbfaca0ac2eb943663ec65316d00e0","tid":97662,"uid":55538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:24:29.000Z","msg":"一齊左年半，分左半年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n間歇性放唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c7e5ef9a7ef4e200ce9e6ec2288f3ca5dbef9e","tid":97662,"uid":14015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊左年半，分左半年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n間歇性放唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢排仲會失眠，訓唔到真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"5afc09b27327d2fb25338d88bdcdfddf72b5ab78","tid":97662,"uid":55538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:31:10.000Z","msg":"可能最近知佢有對象，係無人既時候諗同佢既回憶諗到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b126193b364b73909c084f962f08489b9a288adb","tid":97662,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"一齊左兩年幾，分左一年半<br />\n還是會想起他<br />\n回憶好珍貴<br />\n但再無以後"},{"pid":"46eba68436ecccca239ac5f0a7f834dc1535346d","tid":97662,"uid":61640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"有時真係分唔清楚自己係掛住段回憶定係個人"},{"pid":"d5767feb73cc07363481be14e5c4c497c540345b","tid":97662,"uid":14015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時真係分唔清楚自己係掛住段回憶定係個人</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}